posts.post_title: FS: T206 "Rare" Back Lot of 5 - SOLD
posts.post_content:
Trying to stay focused on 'what' I'm collecting, so these are for sale as a single lot.  Five somewhat "rare" T206 backs all graded SGC 10.  Price includes insured delivery; prefer paypal gift (no fees).

Fred Abbott - Cycle 350
Bill Bergen (Catching) - Sovereign 460
John Hummel - Tolstoi
Orval Overall (Portrait) - El Principe De Gales
Fred Snodgrass (Catching) - Piedmont 350-460 Factory 42
